moviePlot: Nine years after Jesse and Celine first met they encounter each other again on the French leg of Jesse's book tour.
A harried movie director retreats into his memories and fantasies.
Two stage magicians engage in competitive one-upmanship in an attempt to create the ultimate stage illusion.

A young man is accidentally sent thirty years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his friend, Dr. Emmett Brown, and must make sure his high-school-age parents unite in order to save his own existence.
A troubled teenager is plagued by visions of a large bunny rabbit that manipulates him to commit a series of crimes, after narrowly escaping a bizarre accident.
After Homer accidentally pollutes the town's water supply Springfield is encased in a gigantic dome by the EPA and the Simpson family are declared fugitives.
A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

The story of King George VI of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland, his impromptu ascension to the throne and the speech therapist who helped the unsure monarch become worthy of it.

movieName: In the Name of the Father
moviePlot: A man's coerced confession to an IRA bombing he did not commit results in the imprisonment of his father as well. An English lawyer fights to free them.
A nurse is put in charge of an actress who can't talk and finds that the actress's persona is melding with hers.
Two boys growing up in a violent neighborhood of Rio de Janeiro take different paths: one becomes a photographer, the other a drug dealer.
A promising young drummer enrolls at a cut-throat music conservatory where his dreams of greatness are mentored by an instructor who will stop at nothing to realize a student's potential.
Belle, whose father is imprisoned by the Beast, offers herself instead, unaware her captor to be an enchanted prince.
Following the death of a publishing tycoon, news reporters scramble to discover the meaning of his final utterance.

In future Britain, charismatic delinquent Alex DeLarge is jailed and volunteers for an experimental aversion therapy developed by the government in an effort to solve society's crime problem - but not all goes according to plan.
A Polish Jewish musician struggles to survive the destruction of the Warsaw ghetto of World War II.

movieName: Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade
moviePlot: When Dr. Henry Jones Sr. suddenly goes missing while pursuing the Holy Grail, eminent archaeologist Indiana Jones must follow in his father's footsteps and stop the Nazis.
When his secret bride is executed for assaulting an English soldier who tried to rape her, William Wallace begins a revolt against King Edward I of England.

movieName: The Treasure of the Sierra Madre
moviePlot: Fred Dobbs and Bob Curtin, two Americans searching for work in Mexico, convince an old prospector to help them mine for gold in the Sierra Madre Mountains.
